OL,3,C'Tantamount to torture': US prisoner
OL,4,Cexecuted by nitrogen gas
OL,6,FAn American prisoner has been executed
OL,7,Fby inhaling nitrogen gas ` only the
OL,8,Fsecond inmate in the United States'
OL,9,Fhistory to be killed this way.
OL,11,FAlan Eugene Miller shook and trembled
OL,12,Ffor several minutes as he was put to
OL,13,Fdeath in Alabama on Thursday evening.
OL,15,FThe 59-year-old has been on death row
OL,16,Fsince 2000 for shooting dead three
OL,17,Fmale colleagues - Lee Holdbrooks,
OL,18,FChristopher Scott Yancy and Terry
OL,19,FJarvis - a year earlier, believing
OL,20,Fthey were spreading rumours about him
OL,21,Fat work.
