OL,3,C'Tantamount to torture': US prisoner
OL,4,Cexecuted by nitrogen gas
OL,6,FMiller had always sought to be killed
OL,7,Fby nitrogen gas and had even
OL,8,Fundertaken legal proceedings to
OL,9,Fchallenge the state's nitrogen hypoxia
OL,10,Fprotocol to achieve that.
OL,12,F"I didn't do anything to be in here,"
OL,13,FMiller said in his final words, which
OL,14,Fwere muffled by a mask that covered
OL,15,Fhis face from forehead to chin.
OL,17,FCritics have called the method
OL,18,F'tantamount to torture'.
