OL,3,C'Tantamount to torture': US prisoner
OL,4,Cexecuted by nitrogen gas
OL,6,FThe mask was fitted - and re-adjusted
OL,7,F- for about 15 minutes as the nitrogen
OL,8,Fgas flowed.
OL,10,FMiller shook and trembled on a gurney
OL,11,Ffor about two minutes while his body
OL,12,Falso pulled against restraints.
OL,14,FThe shaking and trembling was followed
OL,15,Fby about six minutes of periodic
OL,16,Fgulping breaths before Miller became
OL,17,Fstill.
OL,19,FAlabama Department of Corrections
OL,20,FCommissioner John Hamm said all went
OL,21,Fto plan.
