OL,6,F"There's going to be involuntary body
OL,7,Fmovements as the body is depleted of
OL,8,Foxygen. That is nothing we did not
OL,9,Fexpect," he said.
OL,11,F"Everything went according to plan and
OL,12,Faccording to our protocol, so it went
OL,13,Fjust as we had planned."
OL,15,FTwo years ago, Alabama officials tried
OL,16,Fto put Miller to death by lethal
OL,17,Finjection but failed because they
OL,18,Fcould not access his veins within the
OL,19,Frequired time limit.
