OL,3,C'Tantamount to torture': US prisoner
OL,4,Cexecuted by nitrogen gas
OL,6,FThe first execution by nitrogen
OL,7,Fhypoxia happened earlier this year
OL,8,Fwhen Alabama executed Kenneth Smith.
OL,10,FWitnesses said Smith was shaking and
OL,11,Fwrithing on the gurney for minutes
OL,12,Fbefore he died.
OL,14,FThe United Nations have "unequivocally
OL,15,Fcondemned" the method, saying it is
OL,16,Fnothing short of "state-sanctioned
OL,17,Ftorture".
