OL,6,F"The use, for the first time in humans
OL,7,Fand on an experimental basis, of a
OL,8,Fmethod of execution that has been
OL,9,Fshown to cause suffering in animals is
OL,10,Fsimply outrageous," the UN experts
OL,11,Fsaid following Smith's death earlier
OL,12,Fthis year.
OL,14,FThe states of Louisiana, Oklahoma and
OL,15,FMississippi have also authorised death
OL,16,Fby nitrogen hypoxia.
OL,18,FMiller had nine visitors in his final
OL,19,Fhours and a meal of hamburger steak,
OL,20,Fbaked potato and French fries.
