OL,11,FAlabama Attorney General Steve
OL,12,FMarshall said the execution of Miller
OL,13,F"went as expected and without
OL,14,Fincident".
OL,16,F"Despite misinformation campaigns by
OL,17,Fpolitical activists, out-of-state
OL,18,Flawyers, and biased media, the state
OL,19,Fproved once again that nitrogen
OL,20,Fhypoxia is both humane and effective,"
OL,21,Fhe said in a statement.
